Package com.company

Class Cpu

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.company.Cpu

  • public class Cpu
extends java.lang.Object
    Cpu class manages the fetch and execute cycle and everything necessary for managing that correctly ie. memory, registers, flags, and instructions.
